  "summary": "Mattermost Server Improper Access Control ",
  "details": "Improper Access Control in Mattermost Server versions 9.5.x before 9.5.2, 9.4.x before 9.4.4, 9.3.x before 9.3.3, 8.1.x before 8.1.11 lacked proper access control in the `/api/v4/users/me/teams` endpoint allowing a team admin to get the invite ID of their team, thus allowing them to invite users, even if the \"Add Members\" permission was explicitly removed from team admins. \n\n",
